WEBVTT

01:32.330 --> 01:34.950
[How dare you!?]

01:35.009 --> 01:37.979
[Episode 12]

01:38.789 --> 01:40.720
I was waiting for the wrong person.

01:41.560 --> 01:43.220
But she came at the right time.

01:45.560 --> 01:46.620
If she hadn't come,

01:48.220 --> 01:49.810
I would've been dead long ago.

01:49.810 --> 01:50.890
Am I too stupid,

01:51.410 --> 01:53.340
or did you not make yourself clear?

01:54.710 --> 01:55.770
You're too stupid.

01:56.470 --> 01:57.800
You like her, don't you?

02:01.480 --> 02:03.710
Calling it "like" would be too limiting.

02:03.710 --> 02:05.170
So you don't like her then?

02:20.430 --> 02:22.070
If you don't like her,
that makes things easier.

02:22.070 --> 02:24.430
Since the Master won't let her stay
by your side,

02:24.430 --> 02:26.030
and you won't let me kill her,

02:26.340 --> 02:28.240
I'll just take her away. Problem solved.

02:28.240 --> 02:29.710
She won't go with you.

02:31.430 --> 02:32.400
Don't be so sure.

02:33.310 --> 02:35.910
With my charming good looks
and dashing style,

02:36.180 --> 02:38.180
no beauty could possibly resist me.

02:39.620 --> 02:40.620
Just wait and see.

03:01.150 --> 03:02.080
Can I have this?

03:02.480 --> 03:04.140
This one is already withered.

03:04.400 --> 03:05.310
Its leaves

03:06.400 --> 03:08.060
still show some signs of life.

03:09.560 --> 03:10.560
Just as you said—

03:11.560 --> 03:13.560
if someone makes an effort for it...

03:15.000 --> 03:17.530
who's to say
it can't find the will to survive?

03:18.280 --> 03:19.460
Imperial Physician, please hurry.

03:19.460 --> 03:21.630
Her Highness has been coughing all night
and couldn't sleep.

03:21.630 --> 03:22.090
Coming.

03:31.030 --> 03:33.690
Your Highness,
the imperial physician is here.

03:34.590 --> 03:35.520
This subject...

03:45.630 --> 03:47.800
This subject pays his respects to
Your Highness.

03:47.800 --> 03:48.800
That rainy night,

03:49.470 --> 03:50.910
I failed to recognize Your Highness.

03:50.910 --> 03:52.190
I deserve to die for this offense.

03:52.190 --> 03:54.590
Please punish me
as Your Highness sees fit.

03:55.560 --> 03:57.090
If you keep kneeling there,

03:57.450 --> 03:58.829
I'll never get better.

03:59.190 --> 03:59.920
I'm at fault.

04:00.130 --> 04:01.860
I shall take your pulse at once.

04:10.320 --> 04:11.600
Imperial Physician, please sit.

04:11.600 --> 04:12.200
Thank you.

04:17.250 --> 04:18.110
Your Highness.

04:32.159 --> 04:33.290
How's my condition?

04:39.350 --> 04:41.000
Your Highness's pulse is stable.

04:41.000 --> 04:42.000
Nothing serious.

04:42.720 --> 04:44.600
It's likely from
getting caught in the rain that day,

04:44.600 --> 04:45.720
which allowed external pathogens
to invade your lungs

04:45.720 --> 04:47.270
and disrupt your defensive qi.

04:47.270 --> 04:48.750
I'll prepare some medicine

04:48.750 --> 04:50.530
and have it delivered daily
for Your Highness to take.

04:50.530 --> 04:52.659
You should recover in a couple of days.

04:52.930 --> 04:53.530
Thank you.

05:00.690 --> 05:01.620
May I ask

05:01.930 --> 05:03.730
your name, Imperial Physician?

05:04.430 --> 05:05.830
My name is Xiao Tiancai.

05:08.780 --> 05:09.830
Tiny Genius?

05:10.700 --> 05:11.310
Yes.

05:13.200 --> 05:14.440
Your name

05:14.770 --> 05:15.820
is quite unique.

05:18.020 --> 05:20.440
It's the first time anyone has said so.

05:21.270 --> 05:23.800
Thank you for the compliment,
Your Highness.

05:35.870 --> 05:36.240
Your Highness.

05:36.240 --> 05:37.070
-Your Highness.
-Your Highness.

05:37.070 --> 05:37.560
You...

05:38.360 --> 05:38.820
What...

05:40.850 --> 05:41.510
Don't move!

05:46.050 --> 05:46.730
Bai?

05:47.000 --> 05:47.800
What kind of move was that?

05:47.800 --> 05:49.240
Women's self-defense technique.

05:49.240 --> 05:50.159
Awesome.

05:51.300 --> 05:52.830
That's the only move I know.

05:53.640 --> 05:55.300
You all should practice hard.

05:55.350 --> 05:57.750
Your martial arts aren't even
as good as your mistress's.

05:57.750 --> 05:59.240
Weren't you with His Majesty?

05:59.240 --> 06:00.280
Why are you here?

06:00.430 --> 06:01.090
I originally

06:01.090 --> 06:02.870
meant to spar with Master Bei,

06:03.000 --> 06:04.860
but I couldn't find him anywhere.

06:04.960 --> 06:05.840
So I had to

06:06.130 --> 06:08.370
practice my martial arts
with them instead.

06:08.370 --> 06:09.450
Mr. Bei?

06:09.920 --> 06:11.120
He's in the backyard,

06:11.140 --> 06:12.420
by the stone table.

06:14.620 --> 06:17.220
Isn't there only an old maid
by the stone table?

06:17.870 --> 06:18.780
Mr. Bei.

06:18.920 --> 06:19.800
Wanyin.

06:20.120 --> 06:20.770
Come on, come on.

06:20.770 --> 06:24.500
Look at the embroidery I made—
mandarin ducks playing on the water.

06:24.630 --> 06:25.260
How is it?

06:29.510 --> 06:30.930
You're "Mr. Bei"?

06:35.270 --> 06:37.680
Why are you dressed like this?

06:39.850 --> 06:41.190
So you have

06:41.370 --> 06:43.620
some secret hobbies, huh?

06:43.960 --> 06:45.120
Why are you here?

06:45.380 --> 06:46.670
And this embroidery of yours.

06:46.670 --> 06:48.540
You call those mandarin ducks
playing on the water?

06:48.540 --> 06:51.040
That's clearly a pair of chickens
flapping around.

06:51.040 --> 06:52.500
Am I right, Your Highness?

06:54.370 --> 06:55.070
Wanyin,

06:59.100 --> 07:00.450
let me teach

07:00.560 --> 07:02.750
this disrespectful little disciple
a lesson.

07:02.750 --> 07:04.710
-Mr. Bei, I was only joking.
-Go.

07:09.990 --> 07:11.450
Not the face! Not the face!

07:25.070 --> 07:26.870
Why were you being so sarcastic?

07:30.730 --> 07:31.330
Just

07:32.230 --> 07:33.630
trying to make you smile.

07:37.210 --> 07:37.620
Bai.

07:38.540 --> 07:40.360
You've been roaming the world
for so many years.

07:40.360 --> 07:41.940
You must have been to many places, right?

07:41.940 --> 07:42.890
Of course.

07:44.060 --> 07:46.690
I've seen sunsets over long rivers,
clouds over high mountains,

07:46.690 --> 07:48.830
thousand-year-old temples,
and beacon towers stretching for miles.

07:48.830 --> 07:49.950
Your Highness, just name a place.

07:49.950 --> 07:52.480
Let's see if there's anywhere
I haven't been.

07:53.640 --> 07:54.640
I envy you so much.

07:57.190 --> 07:58.470
What about you, Your Highness?

07:58.470 --> 07:59.600
Where have you been?

08:01.570 --> 08:02.630
I...

08:09.110 --> 08:11.810
Apart from Zhaoyang Palace,
I've only been to Yongyan Hall

08:11.810 --> 08:13.210
and the Imperial Garden.

08:14.980 --> 08:17.310
I don't think I've been outside the palace

08:17.840 --> 08:18.900
since entering it.

08:21.170 --> 08:22.430
That's so boring.

08:26.190 --> 08:27.650
A spirited beauty like you

08:27.950 --> 08:29.550
shouldn't be confined here.

08:30.210 --> 08:31.340
Why not come with me?

08:31.360 --> 08:34.690
I'll take you to see mountains and waters,
to chase sunsets.

08:34.900 --> 08:35.770
Right now?

08:36.120 --> 08:36.980
Your Highness,

08:37.400 --> 08:38.400
the world outside

08:39.360 --> 08:40.559
is not only beautiful

08:40.840 --> 08:42.440
but also full of the unknown.

08:44.480 --> 08:46.010
I once encountered wild men

08:46.080 --> 08:47.510
in the dense forests of the Southwest.

08:47.510 --> 08:49.510
And on a small island in the East Sea,

08:49.540 --> 08:51.070
I came across giant beasts.

08:51.660 --> 08:53.320
Another time, passing through Wuling,

08:53.320 --> 08:55.030
I followed a stream into a cave,

08:55.030 --> 08:56.000
and when I came out,

08:56.000 --> 08:57.470
I found a village hidden

08:57.600 --> 08:59.020
among flower-covered mountains.

08:59.020 --> 08:59.750
It was full of people

08:59.750 --> 09:02.610
who had been isolated from the world
for centuries.

09:03.590 --> 09:05.190
"The Peach Blossom Spring"?

09:06.200 --> 09:08.870
How did you know
those flowers were peach blossoms?

09:08.870 --> 09:09.560
Well...

09:09.580 --> 09:11.540
Anyway, when the wind blew,

09:11.670 --> 09:13.530
petals fell everywhere

09:13.630 --> 09:14.940
like pink snow.

09:15.630 --> 09:16.630
I'll never forget

09:17.440 --> 09:19.300
that sight for the rest of my life.

09:20.310 --> 09:21.540
If I ever get the chance,

09:21.540 --> 09:23.340
I'd really love to see it myself.

09:24.550 --> 09:25.610
Wuling is far away,

09:26.050 --> 09:27.850
but I can show it to you right now.

09:32.060 --> 09:34.260
♪ A letter, a line of words ♪

09:34.470 --> 09:35.690
♪ Picking up the pen again and again ♪

09:36.070 --> 09:38.220
♪ A cup of tea, a glass of wine ♪

09:38.580 --> 09:40.000
♪ Drinking alone, hard to get drunk ♪

09:40.040 --> 09:42.360
♪ Words unspoken ♪

09:43.970 --> 09:46.340
♪ Shyness unhidden ♪

09:48.090 --> 09:50.270
♪ Walking down a street together ♪

09:50.570 --> 09:51.610
♪ Shoulder to shoulder ♪

09:52.110 --> 09:54.070
♪ Raising my head, lowering my eyes ♪

09:54.590 --> 09:55.940
♪ Blushing slightly ♪

09:56.050 --> 09:58.460
♪ A face flushed red at first sight ♪

10:00.050 --> 10:03.490
♪ A smile like a flower in my heart ♪

10:03.990 --> 10:07.250
♪ Whose longing lingers day and night? ♪

10:08.050 --> 10:10.980
♪ Piling up stories
and countless thoughts ♪

10:11.470 --> 10:13.310
♪ Walking through once, taking a glance ♪

10:13.480 --> 10:15.080
♪ All lingering and wandering ♪

10:15.420 --> 10:17.130
♪ How many rains, how many winds? ♪

10:17.430 --> 10:19.530
♪ Looking back, it's all like smoke ♪

10:20.010 --> 10:23.160
♪ Watching the hazy world ♪

10:23.980 --> 10:26.310
♪ Who still guards that yearning? ♪

10:26.380 --> 10:27.520
♪ Still unchanged ♪

10:27.990 --> 10:30.800
♪ Even if months and years
pass in a blink ♪

10:31.450 --> 10:32.900
♪ One thought for a lifetime ♪

10:33.010 --> 10:37.390
♪ Waiting for someone to appear ♪

10:51.910 --> 10:55.440
♪ Whose longing lingers day and night? ♪

10:55.640 --> 10:56.480
Why are you here?

10:55.990 --> 10:58.930
♪ Piling up stories
and countless thoughts ♪

10:57.470 --> 10:58.800
To have dinner with you.

10:59.520 --> 11:01.370
♪ Walking through once, taking a glance ♪

11:01.520 --> 11:03.160
♪ All lingering and wandering ♪

11:03.510 --> 11:05.180
♪ How many rains, how many winds? ♪

11:05.450 --> 11:07.560
♪ Looking back, it's all like smoke ♪

11:08.000 --> 11:11.210
♪ Watching the hazy world ♪

11:11.980 --> 11:14.390
♪ Who still guards that yearning? ♪

11:12.360 --> 11:14.090
All the effort, down the drain.

11:14.510 --> 11:15.560
♪ Still unchanged ♪

11:16.020 --> 11:18.930
♪ Even if months and years
pass in a blink ♪

11:18.200 --> 11:18.860
Don't move.

11:19.480 --> 11:20.930
♪ One thought for a lifetime ♪

11:20.990 --> 11:28.340
♪ Waiting for someone to appear ♪

11:38.150 --> 11:39.150
All of you, leave.

11:50.310 --> 11:51.030
Then I'll just dig in.

11:51.030 --> 11:51.560
Go ahead.

11:54.130 --> 11:55.220
Smells so good!

11:56.150 --> 11:57.810
Get me a bowl and chopsticks, will you?

11:57.810 --> 11:58.860
Imperial Guards!

11:59.200 --> 12:00.130
Don't call them.

12:00.810 --> 12:02.000
I won't be freeloading.

12:02.000 --> 12:04.930
I'll give you intelligence on Yan State
in exchange.

12:05.170 --> 12:05.780
Deal?

12:10.020 --> 12:12.610
Situated between grasslands and desert,

12:12.910 --> 12:15.790
they live at nature's mercy
and love causing trouble.

12:15.790 --> 12:17.910
They pillage, burn, and plunder—

12:17.930 --> 12:21.430
strong in body but lacking honor.

12:22.660 --> 12:23.650
What I'm talking about

12:23.650 --> 12:25.630
[Yan] [Stealing]

12:24.480 --> 12:25.440
is the Yan State.

12:25.840 --> 12:28.790
They don't just steal food, horses,
and cloth—

12:27.640 --> 12:32.520
[Yan] [Stealing] [Xia]

12:28.820 --> 12:29.550
they even...

12:30.120 --> 12:31.510
want to take over

12:31.750 --> 12:32.610
our entire Xia.

12:36.060 --> 12:37.150
I'd like to ask

12:37.680 --> 12:39.680
about the royal family of Yan State.

12:39.860 --> 12:47.150
[Zhaluowahan, Emperor of Yan]

12:41.840 --> 12:43.820
Zhaluowahan is the emperor of Yan,

12:44.250 --> 12:46.680
cunning and deceitful behind his smile.

12:48.120 --> 12:53.130
[Zhaluowahan, Emperor of Yan]
[Prince Tu'er]

12:48.910 --> 12:50.910
Prince Tu'er is busy on the battlefield,

12:50.910 --> 12:51.970
proud of his talent

12:52.380 --> 12:53.360
to the point of arrogance.

12:53.360 --> 12:54.960
Your Highness, please look.

12:57.380 --> 13:00.180
[Zhaluowahan, Emperor of Yan]

12:57.840 --> 12:59.610
They're uncle and nephew,

12:59.830 --> 13:00.990
but actually rivals.

13:00.180 --> 13:01.010
[Prince Tu'er]

13:01.630 --> 13:02.710
Apart from both hating our empire,

13:02.710 --> 13:05.040
they can't see eye to eye
on anything else.

13:06.650 --> 13:07.860
Between these two,

13:07.880 --> 13:09.410
who would be easier to turn?

13:11.510 --> 13:13.200
Actually, neither is very likely.

13:13.200 --> 13:15.270
The Emperor of Yan lost an eye
to our arrow.

13:15.270 --> 13:16.200
As for Tu'er...

13:17.080 --> 13:18.110
he has some

13:18.440 --> 13:20.300
old grievances with His Majesty.

13:20.790 --> 13:21.520
Grievances?

13:21.870 --> 13:22.870
What grievances?

13:25.720 --> 13:26.630
Should I

13:26.790 --> 13:28.050
not have brought up...

13:30.750 --> 13:32.150
Beautiful Lady Shanyi?

13:35.480 --> 13:37.080
Your Highness, please look.

13:39.140 --> 13:40.740
Beautiful Lady Shanyi?

13:41.790 --> 13:42.840
Who is she?

13:42.860 --> 13:44.660
Tu'er's childhood sweetheart.

13:45.930 --> 13:48.340
Years ago, the Emperor of Yan sent her
to dance in the palace,

13:48.340 --> 13:50.000
where she caused quite a stir.

13:50.030 --> 13:50.480
Later,

13:51.080 --> 13:53.410
she was granted the title of
Beautiful Lady.

13:53.410 --> 13:54.470
But not long after,

13:54.630 --> 13:56.780
[Beautiful Lady Shanyi]

13:54.730 --> 13:56.480
she was accused of attempting to
assassinate the Emperor

13:56.480 --> 13:58.490
under the pretext of
attending the bedchamber

13:58.490 --> 13:59.530
and was executed.

14:00.240 --> 14:01.600
Yan State used this as an excuse

14:01.600 --> 14:02.800
to declare war on Xia,

14:03.200 --> 14:04.510
fighting for many years.

14:04.510 --> 14:05.910
I didn't know about this.

14:08.550 --> 14:09.010
Then...

14:09.740 --> 14:11.070
how do you know all this?

14:11.630 --> 14:12.600
No matter what,

14:12.760 --> 14:14.920
we should send someone
to talk with them separately.

14:14.920 --> 14:16.790
Peace negotiations are crucial
for our nation.

14:16.790 --> 14:17.720
If either of them

14:18.080 --> 14:19.190
is a wise ruler,

14:20.090 --> 14:22.600
they should know to set aside
personal grudges.

14:22.600 --> 14:23.060
Wanyin,

14:24.130 --> 14:24.990
who do you think

14:25.290 --> 14:26.750
would be suitable to send?

14:30.130 --> 14:33.720
Among the scholars, the one skilled in
diplomacy and fluent in the Yan language

14:33.720 --> 14:34.770
is Wang Zhao.

14:35.800 --> 14:37.210
Gentlemen.

14:39.640 --> 14:40.030
Look.

14:40.390 --> 14:40.840
Wang,

14:40.950 --> 14:42.800
I must say, in this outfit,

14:42.840 --> 14:45.030
you really do look a bit like
someone from Yan State.

14:45.030 --> 14:45.600
Well?

14:45.670 --> 14:46.870
I wore this specially tonight

14:46.870 --> 14:48.210
to show all of you first!

14:48.390 --> 14:49.440
Come on, sit, sit!

14:50.790 --> 14:51.650
Where is Er Lan?

14:51.720 --> 14:52.610
Why isn't he here?

14:52.610 --> 14:53.370
Er Lan...

14:53.740 --> 14:54.840
Tonight...

14:55.550 --> 14:57.360
the Minister of Revenue is
hosting a banquet.

14:57.360 --> 14:57.890
Er Lan...

14:59.550 --> 15:00.440
He...

15:01.510 --> 15:03.030
accepted the invitation and went.

15:03.030 --> 15:04.570
Isn't he just socializing on your behalf?

15:04.570 --> 15:06.050
-What do you mean...
-Er

15:06.550 --> 15:08.350
asked me to bring you some money.

15:08.390 --> 15:09.900
-For the road...
-I can't take it.

15:09.900 --> 15:11.600
His Majesty has already allocated funds.

15:11.600 --> 15:12.640
Why be polite?

15:12.990 --> 15:14.030
It's not my money anyway.

15:14.030 --> 15:15.360
He sent money to him too?

15:16.670 --> 15:17.030
What?

15:17.690 --> 15:19.690
You also brought some money for him?

15:22.000 --> 15:22.550
Wang,

15:22.910 --> 15:23.870
travel rich even if you live poor.

15:23.870 --> 15:24.870
Take this as well.

15:26.550 --> 15:27.350
Thank you, Li.

15:27.690 --> 15:29.750
You talk the most—what did you bring?

15:30.870 --> 15:31.200
Here.

15:32.150 --> 15:34.030
I personally went to Nanshan Temple

15:34.030 --> 15:35.120
to pray and obtain this for you.

15:35.120 --> 15:36.000
When traveling far from home,

15:36.000 --> 15:37.120
ability is one thing,

15:37.120 --> 15:38.920
but luck is also very important!

15:38.960 --> 15:39.420
Come on!

15:39.510 --> 15:40.040
Put it on!

15:40.150 --> 15:40.630
Okay!

15:41.550 --> 15:43.350
It's been blessed by a high monk.

15:44.750 --> 15:46.100
I found a copy

15:46.150 --> 15:48.350
of "The Gazetteer of Yan" for you, Wang.

15:48.600 --> 15:50.950
It contains information about
Yan State's customs and culture.

15:49.100 --> 15:51.240
[The Gazetteer of Yan]

15:51.360 --> 15:52.620
I hope it'll be of help.

15:53.000 --> 15:53.580
Cen,

15:54.790 --> 15:56.520
that's very thoughtful of you.

15:56.720 --> 15:57.120
What's

15:57.620 --> 15:58.800
this flower?

15:59.030 --> 16:00.440
I've never seen it before.

16:00.440 --> 16:01.200
Camel Bell.

16:02.080 --> 16:03.030
Camel Bell?

16:03.670 --> 16:04.470
That's right.

16:05.120 --> 16:06.920
It's a plant unique to Yan State.

16:07.480 --> 16:08.240
Legend has it

16:08.300 --> 16:10.790
that it grew from the tears of camels
who couldn't

16:10.790 --> 16:12.440
bear to part with their beloved.

16:12.440 --> 16:13.470
The people of Yan believe

16:13.470 --> 16:15.390
that those who travel with this flower

16:15.390 --> 16:16.790
will eventually reunite

16:17.360 --> 16:18.620
with their loved ones.

16:23.760 --> 16:25.060
If that's so,

16:25.720 --> 16:27.680
with this flower, Wang,

16:27.840 --> 16:28.680
you'll surely

16:29.200 --> 16:30.460
return safe and sound!

16:30.840 --> 16:31.300
Indeed.

16:31.840 --> 16:32.840
The journey ahead

16:33.000 --> 16:35.120
is long and fraught with difficulties.

16:35.120 --> 16:35.550
Let us

16:35.970 --> 16:37.720
offer this humble cup of wine

16:37.960 --> 16:39.760
to wish you a safe journey, Wang.

16:43.410 --> 16:44.560
May we encourage

16:45.770 --> 16:46.500
one another.

16:54.840 --> 16:57.840
[General Luo, things in the palace
have been peaceful recently.]

16:57.840 --> 17:00.880
[I'm trying to save your son.
You may rest assured.]

17:02.270 --> 17:03.130
Your Highness,

17:03.820 --> 17:05.200
there's news from the palace.

17:05.200 --> 17:06.030
That mysterious martial arts master

17:06.030 --> 17:08.359
at the Emperor's side has appeared again.

17:12.880 --> 17:13.589
Where?

17:14.359 --> 17:15.079
Zhaoyang Palace.

17:15.079 --> 17:16.810
Zhaoyang Palace?

17:22.589 --> 17:23.990
It seems it's time

17:25.069 --> 17:26.880
for me to have a chat

17:27.859 --> 17:28.790
with Consort Yu.

17:49.160 --> 17:50.360
This commoner, Wang Zhao,

17:50.360 --> 17:52.420
pays his respects to Your Majesty...

17:53.110 --> 17:55.070
There are too many eyes and ears around.

17:55.070 --> 17:57.480
Don't bother with
such formalities, Mr. Wang.

17:57.480 --> 18:00.260
To avoid the eyes and ears of
Prince Duan and the Empress Dowager,

18:00.260 --> 18:02.170
you must disguise yourself as a merchant

18:02.170 --> 18:03.460
and travel to Yan State.

18:03.460 --> 18:05.890
I can't give you an official decree
for this journey

18:05.890 --> 18:07.220
nor a legitimate cause.

18:08.290 --> 18:09.960
I can't send guards with you,

18:10.370 --> 18:11.670
only a few secret ones

18:12.770 --> 18:14.300
to protect you discreetly.

18:15.090 --> 18:16.490
Once you reach Yan State,

18:16.810 --> 18:17.870
you'll also need to

18:18.540 --> 18:19.790
play it by ear.

18:20.830 --> 18:22.230
The journey ahead is long

18:23.030 --> 18:24.490
and extremely dangerous.

18:25.300 --> 18:26.310
I hope you will...

18:27.970 --> 18:30.030
take good care of yourself, Mr. Wang.

18:33.410 --> 18:34.810
Thank you, Your Majesty.

18:37.240 --> 18:38.240
This commoner...

18:40.880 --> 18:43.340
This commoner lost his father
at a young age.

18:43.640 --> 18:44.700
My only concern

18:45.630 --> 18:47.000
is my widowed mother at home.

18:47.000 --> 18:48.930
I'll take good care of your mother.

18:49.950 --> 18:51.750
You go for the sake of the nation.

18:52.240 --> 18:52.820
I...

18:54.350 --> 18:56.220
will certainly take care of everything

18:56.220 --> 18:58.150
so you have nothing to worry about.

19:00.340 --> 19:01.860
I will do my utmost

19:02.400 --> 19:03.930
to stop the war and establish trade.

19:03.930 --> 19:04.730
I won't return

19:06.260 --> 19:07.190
until I succeed.

19:12.140 --> 19:13.940
We are counting on you, Mr. Wang.

19:48.920 --> 19:53.300
[Camel Bell]

20:01.030 --> 20:01.960
My Lady!

20:02.770 --> 20:04.270
Just now, an unfamiliar young eunuch

20:04.270 --> 20:05.320
shoved this into my hands.

20:05.320 --> 20:06.610
When I called out to him, he ran away,

20:06.610 --> 20:08.410
and I couldn't catch up with him.

20:16.450 --> 20:19.720
A kindred spirit is hard to find—
why hesitate?

20:20.040 --> 20:22.100
Let's meet at the flower house today.

20:24.880 --> 20:26.010
You may leave first.

20:26.270 --> 20:26.940
Yes.

20:57.200 --> 20:58.640
Prince Duan, you were in such a hurry
to see me.

20:58.640 --> 21:00.300
-What's...
-Wanyin, have you

21:00.440 --> 21:01.700
seen anything lately?

21:02.890 --> 21:03.590
Seen?

21:07.510 --> 21:09.270
Didn't you tell me before

21:10.240 --> 21:13.100
that you could use foresight
to predict the future?

21:15.360 --> 21:16.040
Yes.

21:17.050 --> 21:18.010
I have...

21:18.560 --> 21:20.360
indeed seen some things lately.

21:22.580 --> 21:23.270
Like what?

21:24.350 --> 21:25.370
Like,

21:26.320 --> 21:28.850
in the dense forests of the Southwest,

21:29.050 --> 21:31.180
footprints of wild men have appeared.

21:31.640 --> 21:32.430
And

21:32.980 --> 21:35.670
on a small island in East Lake,

21:36.600 --> 21:39.400
there seem to be giants
swimming in the inner lake.

21:40.580 --> 21:42.670
Following the stream
toward the mountains in Wuling,

21:42.670 --> 21:43.780
I saw light ahead.

21:44.150 --> 21:46.850
Beyond the mountain are hillsides
covered with peach trees.

21:46.850 --> 21:48.000
I've heard

21:48.200 --> 21:52.130
that the martial arts master
by the Emperor's side has appeared again—

21:52.370 --> 21:54.290
and this time, inside the palace.

21:56.250 --> 21:57.780
He has discovered Bei Zhou?

21:58.790 --> 22:00.920
It's very dangerous
if we don't eliminate this guy.

22:00.920 --> 22:02.510
Can you help me foresee

22:03.480 --> 22:05.180
how we can get rid of him?

22:05.690 --> 22:07.420
Is this information reliable?

22:07.910 --> 22:09.770
How did Your Highness learn of it?

22:12.920 --> 22:14.040
I saw it in my dream

22:15.560 --> 22:17.090
using my foresight as well.

22:19.950 --> 22:22.020
You just said you "heard" about it.

22:22.750 --> 22:23.960
You bastard—

22:24.310 --> 22:26.470
lying without even
preparing your story properly.

22:26.470 --> 22:29.270
Is that Imperial Physician Xiao
competent or not?

22:29.280 --> 22:31.130
When others are sick,
the physicians tell them to stay in bed,

22:31.130 --> 22:32.860
yet he encourages you to go out.

22:34.810 --> 22:36.210
The sunshine is perfect.

22:36.830 --> 22:38.270
Some moderate sun exposure

22:38.270 --> 22:39.870
is beneficial for recovery.

22:41.110 --> 22:43.580
Still, there's no need to come all the way
to the flower house.

22:43.580 --> 22:45.550
I dropped an earring when I was sheltering
from the rain the other day.

22:45.550 --> 22:46.880
It might be somewhere in the flower house.

22:46.880 --> 22:48.010
Let's go look for it.

22:49.680 --> 22:50.540
My Lady,

22:50.700 --> 22:52.310
isn't that Prince Duan and...

22:52.310 --> 22:53.670
Why are they together?

23:02.660 --> 23:03.190
Wanyin.

23:05.880 --> 23:07.340
Are you willing to help me?

23:08.300 --> 23:09.580
Prince Duan, please wait a moment.

23:09.580 --> 23:10.640
Let me give it a try.

23:15.480 --> 23:17.810
Now both Bei Zhou and Bai are
in the palace,

23:18.590 --> 23:20.520
yet he only knows of one master,

23:21.060 --> 23:22.210
not two.

23:30.400 --> 23:31.410
I saw...

23:33.590 --> 23:35.820
what seemed to be a tall man

23:36.510 --> 23:38.040
appearing in a corridor.

23:41.030 --> 23:42.000
A corridor?

23:47.590 --> 23:48.740
Which...

23:50.670 --> 23:51.390
corridor?

23:51.530 --> 23:53.130
It seemed to be in the Imperial Garden,

23:53.130 --> 23:54.190
but I can't be sure.

23:55.110 --> 23:57.270
It was too rushed to see clearly.

23:57.810 --> 24:00.100
Have you consulted Consort Xie about it?

24:03.350 --> 24:04.520
I came to you first.

24:06.910 --> 24:09.240
If you can't foresee it within three days,

24:10.740 --> 24:13.300
it won't be too late for me
to ask her then.

24:14.790 --> 24:16.390
Who leaked the information?

24:18.320 --> 24:19.120
Could it be...

24:19.310 --> 24:20.820
Just now, an unfamiliar young eunuch

24:20.820 --> 24:22.020
shoved this into my hands.

24:22.020 --> 24:23.200
When I called out to him, he ran away,

24:23.200 --> 24:25.000
and I couldn't catch up with him.

24:25.120 --> 24:25.850
My Lady.

24:27.410 --> 24:28.820
This isn't the way back to the palace.

24:28.820 --> 24:31.150
I saw you walking this way
with your head down,

24:31.150 --> 24:32.750
so I didn't dare disturb you.

24:39.880 --> 24:40.510
My Lady,

24:41.030 --> 24:42.270
this is flower tea I prepared myself

24:42.270 --> 24:44.030
to clear internal heat and detoxify.

24:44.030 --> 24:45.360
Would you like to try it?

24:46.360 --> 24:47.030
No need.

24:48.310 --> 24:50.070
My Lady, you've been looking worried

24:50.070 --> 24:51.470
ever since you returned.

24:52.830 --> 24:54.430
Is something troubling you?

24:58.550 --> 24:59.920
I just saw Prince Duan,

25:01.040 --> 25:03.100
who apparently offended His Majesty

25:03.790 --> 25:05.190
and was about to be caned.

25:05.930 --> 25:09.190
I overheard His Majesty
instructing the secret guards...

25:09.810 --> 25:12.470
to be especially brutal
during the punishment.

25:12.570 --> 25:13.830
I wonder if Prince Duan

25:15.010 --> 25:16.080
will survive this.

25:16.980 --> 25:18.240
How could this happen?

25:19.990 --> 25:21.590
Should I go ask around?

25:21.790 --> 25:22.650
Are you insane?

25:23.020 --> 25:24.620
If His Majesty catches you at this time,

25:24.620 --> 25:26.680
how am I supposed to explain it to him?

25:28.090 --> 25:30.020
I didn't think it through, My Lady.

25:34.000 --> 25:35.000
You may leave now.

25:45.750 --> 25:46.590
Let go of me!

25:47.000 --> 25:48.390
Let go of me!

25:49.140 --> 25:49.540
Kneel!

25:51.720 --> 25:53.310
Your Highness is most perceptive.

25:53.310 --> 25:54.400
This maid snuck out

25:54.680 --> 25:56.240
to pass information to a eunuch

25:56.240 --> 25:57.240
bribed by Prince Duan.

25:57.240 --> 25:58.590
We apprehended her on the spot.

25:58.590 --> 25:59.570
You're lying!

25:59.930 --> 26:00.640
My Lady.

26:01.000 --> 26:02.850
When did you start
consorting with Prince Duan?

26:02.850 --> 26:04.320
I didn't!

26:05.200 --> 26:07.510
How could I ever dare harbor such thoughts
toward His Highness?

26:07.510 --> 26:08.510
Still denying it?

26:11.000 --> 26:11.750
My Lady,

26:12.790 --> 26:14.510
I was worried
you were concerned about His Highness,

26:14.510 --> 26:16.310
so I went out to find a way to help.

26:16.920 --> 26:17.440
My Lady,

26:18.270 --> 26:20.260
how can you not trust me?

26:22.200 --> 26:24.130
It's because I trusted you too much

26:24.880 --> 26:27.010
that I gave you the chance to betray me.

26:27.750 --> 26:29.150
I've never betrayed you,

26:30.680 --> 26:32.550
and my loyalty has never wavered.

26:32.650 --> 26:33.510
Tell the truth!

26:36.200 --> 26:37.800
It was the Lantern Festival—

26:38.060 --> 26:40.990
the Lantern Festival
before you entered the palace.

26:45.960 --> 26:47.900
I was by your side then,

26:49.470 --> 26:51.270
when you first met His Highness.

26:52.500 --> 26:55.580
I watched the two of you
fall for each other.

26:57.590 --> 26:59.940
You were so happy back then.

27:02.330 --> 27:04.330
After entering the palace with you,

27:04.890 --> 27:07.420
he occasionally came to chat with me.

27:07.440 --> 27:08.530
That's all.

27:18.610 --> 27:20.070
So you've been passing information
about me

27:20.070 --> 27:21.400
to him all along?

27:23.130 --> 27:24.730
I just don't understand...

27:27.510 --> 27:29.270
why you didn't choose His Highness

27:29.270 --> 27:31.000
but chose that tyrant instead.

27:33.080 --> 27:35.650
You used to despise the tyrant.

27:36.440 --> 27:39.100
You cried every day and couldn't eat.

27:39.630 --> 27:42.630
But ever since you suddenly started
attending the tyrant at night,

27:42.630 --> 27:44.030
everything has changed.

27:45.400 --> 27:47.020
I understand even less

27:47.070 --> 27:49.330
why you've clearly fallen for the tyrant

27:49.640 --> 27:51.780
yet still string Prince Duan along,

27:52.930 --> 27:55.390
letting him waste away for you
day after day,

27:56.460 --> 27:59.860
while you only care about
enjoying yourself with the tyrant.

28:02.750 --> 28:04.950
So the day I left the palace in disguise—

28:05.670 --> 28:07.670
it was also you who told Prince Duan?

28:07.940 --> 28:08.690
It was me.

28:12.200 --> 28:15.440
But that day, Master Yu had just been
framed by Consort Shu's family,

28:15.440 --> 28:18.410
and then His Majesty immediately took you
out of the palace.

28:18.410 --> 28:20.320
I was worried about your safety.

28:22.750 --> 28:25.950
It just so happened
that His Highness sent someone to ask,

28:26.460 --> 28:27.640
so I told them

28:27.670 --> 28:29.560
which gate you left from.

28:34.350 --> 28:35.200
Your Highness,

28:35.200 --> 28:36.200
shall we kill her?

28:40.110 --> 28:41.130
My Lady...

28:42.430 --> 28:43.220
My Lady!

28:46.110 --> 28:48.110
I entered your household at age five

28:48.210 --> 28:49.420
to serve you.

28:50.680 --> 28:53.740
We ate and slept together,
and I cared about everything about you.

28:53.740 --> 28:56.700
You must believe I would never harm you.

28:57.090 --> 28:59.820
Everything I did was for your sake,

28:59.850 --> 29:00.880
My Lady.

29:28.360 --> 29:29.960
Take her back and lock her up.

29:31.960 --> 29:33.290
Without my permission,

29:34.240 --> 29:35.240
don't let her out.

29:35.310 --> 29:36.070
My Lady!

29:36.440 --> 29:37.240
My Lady...

29:37.960 --> 29:40.620
The tyrant demoted Master Yu
and neglected you!

29:41.240 --> 29:43.440
My Lady, you need to come to your senses!

30:47.310 --> 30:49.110
I've just returned to the palace

30:49.510 --> 30:51.710
and heard about what happened with Mei.

30:52.750 --> 30:53.680
Are you alright?

31:04.850 --> 31:06.710
I've been thinking for a long time

31:06.780 --> 31:07.980
and just remembered.

31:10.440 --> 31:13.590
In the novel, the original female lead
lost her mother at a young age

31:13.590 --> 31:15.320
and grew up without affection.

31:15.580 --> 31:16.890
When she was eight,

31:18.280 --> 31:20.480
she caught highly contagious measles.

31:21.470 --> 31:24.130
Everyone in the household
kept their distance.

31:25.370 --> 31:27.700
They locked me in a cold,
damp side chamber

31:28.050 --> 31:29.310
and just left me there.

31:30.050 --> 31:32.080
Only Mei voluntarily stayed with me

31:32.840 --> 31:33.940
and took care of me.

31:37.490 --> 31:38.190
Wanyin.

31:40.970 --> 31:42.830
You didn't go through any of that.

31:43.460 --> 31:45.120
Don't think about it anymore.

31:46.160 --> 31:47.820
But I've been here for so long,

31:48.720 --> 31:50.520
and she's been really good to me.

31:50.620 --> 31:51.350
Listen to me,

31:51.850 --> 31:53.910
you inexplicably entered this book,

31:54.060 --> 31:56.120
into a completely unfamiliar world.

31:57.270 --> 31:59.400
Not only did you have to adapt quickly,

31:59.400 --> 32:01.010
but you also had to constantly think about

32:01.010 --> 32:02.610
how to deal with Prince Duan,

32:02.660 --> 32:04.260
handle the Empress Dowager,

32:04.610 --> 32:06.010
and struggle to survive.

32:07.440 --> 32:09.500
You've already been doing very well.

32:10.910 --> 32:12.510
Better than I have, at least.

32:14.410 --> 32:15.140
Without you,

32:16.720 --> 32:18.520
I might not have made it this far.

32:19.980 --> 32:22.080
I completely understand why you're upset

32:22.080 --> 32:23.050
about Mei.

32:24.660 --> 32:26.250
But don't ever

32:26.800 --> 32:27.840
doubt yourself.

32:29.170 --> 32:30.430
Don't blame yourself.

32:32.330 --> 32:33.050
Alright?

32:34.400 --> 32:36.130
Have I really done well enough?

32:41.900 --> 32:43.120
But I'm so tired.

32:50.320 --> 32:51.920
Let me lean on you for a while.

32:53.600 --> 32:56.000
Just a moment,
and I'll be fully recharged.

33:02.180 --> 33:04.240
Mei can't stay in the palace anymore.

33:05.590 --> 33:07.520
I'll find a chance to send her away.

33:30.750 --> 33:32.040
What time is it now?

33:32.470 --> 33:33.330
Just past 9 AM.

33:36.110 --> 33:37.570
How did I sleep for so long?

33:44.750 --> 33:45.610
What about Mei?

33:46.000 --> 33:46.930
Has she been fed?

33:47.990 --> 33:48.850
Yes, she has.

33:50.350 --> 33:51.160
Your Highness,

33:51.160 --> 33:52.960
would you like to go check on Mei?

33:54.240 --> 33:56.140
She kept saying this morning

33:56.510 --> 33:58.310
that she wanted to see you again.

34:01.130 --> 34:02.790
She also left a letter for you.

34:04.720 --> 34:08.300
[To My Lady, personally]

34:16.030 --> 34:16.810
[My Lady,
I know you're still angry with me.]

34:16.840 --> 34:17.670
[Although you are my mistress,
all these years,]

34:17.699 --> 34:18.420
[I've long regarded you as family—]

34:18.449 --> 34:19.600
[the only person I care about
in this world.]

34:20.760 --> 34:21.620
Your Highness,

34:21.670 --> 34:23.480
I was ordered to
escort Mei out of the palace,

34:23.480 --> 34:24.080
but she...

34:24.630 --> 34:25.090
is gone.

34:33.230 --> 34:34.010
My Lady,

34:34.480 --> 34:36.340
I know you're still angry with me.

34:36.550 --> 34:39.080
Please let me call you "My Lady"
one last time.

34:40.110 --> 34:41.570
From now on in this palace,

34:42.030 --> 34:44.280
everyone will only address you as
"Your Highness,"

34:44.280 --> 34:47.340
-and no one will call you "My Lady".
-My Lady, you're up.

34:48.070 --> 34:49.730
Although you are my mistress,

34:49.840 --> 34:50.840
all these years,

34:51.320 --> 34:53.179
I've long regarded you as family—

34:54.360 --> 34:56.690
the only person I care about
in this world.

34:57.480 --> 34:59.030
This morning, His Majesty ordered me
to leave the palace.

34:59.030 --> 34:59.760
My Lady!

34:59.760 --> 35:00.690
But without you,

35:01.230 --> 35:02.150
I'm nothing but

35:02.150 --> 35:04.590
-a wandering soul with nowhere to go.
-My Lady!

35:04.590 --> 35:07.360
Life has no meaning for me anymore.

35:07.970 --> 35:08.850
Before I die,

35:09.510 --> 35:11.770
let this servant do one last thing for you

35:12.190 --> 35:13.670
to repay your kindness.

35:15.480 --> 35:16.940
Whether I succeed or fail,

35:17.160 --> 35:18.690
I can only be your maid again

35:19.280 --> 35:20.590
in the next life.

35:50.360 --> 35:51.110
Yu Wanyin,

35:51.420 --> 35:53.070
you actually let that maid of yours,

35:53.070 --> 35:55.330
-M...
-The Empress Dowager has arrived!

35:58.670 --> 36:00.130
Greetings, Your Majesty.

36:03.230 --> 36:03.960
Consort Shu,

36:04.380 --> 36:05.110
are you hurt?

36:05.440 --> 36:08.100
Your Majesty, you must stand up for me.

36:08.170 --> 36:10.150
I was just strolling here

36:10.270 --> 36:11.150
when that girl called...

36:11.150 --> 36:11.920
Mei,

36:11.950 --> 36:13.080
yes, Mei,

36:13.100 --> 36:14.190
suddenly rushed out

36:14.190 --> 36:16.030
with scissors, trying to stab me,

36:16.030 --> 36:17.540
shouting something about

36:17.620 --> 36:18.950
how I ordered my brother

36:18.970 --> 36:20.540
to harm Noble Consort Yu's father.

36:20.540 --> 36:21.950
And just now, Juan

36:22.030 --> 36:23.190
stepped in to protect me

36:23.190 --> 36:24.990
and got this huge cut on her hand.

36:29.310 --> 36:30.690
How dare you, Noble Consort Yu.

36:30.690 --> 36:33.820
Do you have any idea
what kind of disaster you've caused?

36:34.440 --> 36:36.590
Noble Consort Yu has become arrogant
from His Majesty's favor

36:36.590 --> 36:38.250
and now disregards all rules.

36:38.280 --> 36:39.060
She shall be demoted from

36:39.060 --> 36:40.280
Noble Consort to Concubine!

36:40.280 --> 36:40.880
Guards,

36:41.360 --> 36:42.030
take her to the Cold Palace.

36:42.030 --> 36:42.280
-Yes, Your Majesty!
-Yes, Your Majesty!

36:42.280 --> 36:44.010
Await the Emperor's judgment.

36:44.860 --> 36:45.540
Mei!

36:59.050 --> 37:01.370
Zhang San's Diary.

37:03.770 --> 37:05.460
Your Highness, please hurry.

37:10.480 --> 37:12.050
Let go of me!

37:12.320 --> 37:13.590
Let go of me!

37:13.690 --> 37:14.750
Hold Her Majesty down firmly!

37:14.750 --> 37:16.750
Don't let Her Majesty hurt herself!

37:16.810 --> 37:17.630
Tie her tight!

37:17.770 --> 37:19.130
Let go of me!

37:19.570 --> 37:20.500
It hurts!

37:21.980 --> 37:22.610
Let go of me!

37:22.610 --> 37:23.730
The water is too cold! Change it!

37:23.730 --> 37:24.610
Let go of me!

37:25.540 --> 37:25.980
It hurts...

37:25.980 --> 37:26.580
Hurry, hurry!

37:26.580 --> 37:28.240
-Hold here!
-It's killing me!

37:29.060 --> 37:30.990
Don't just stand there. Come help!

37:32.820 --> 37:35.220
-Let go of me!
-Hold her down! Hold her down!

37:38.680 --> 37:40.480
-Noble Consort.
-Hurry, hurry!

37:40.700 --> 37:41.500
Crown Prince,

37:42.370 --> 37:43.300
don't be afraid.

37:44.830 --> 37:46.060
Hold her down!

37:57.580 --> 37:58.390
Mother,

37:58.810 --> 38:00.360
Mother, are you alright?

38:00.650 --> 38:02.690
When I came to pay my respects yesterday,

38:02.690 --> 38:04.290
weren't you perfectly fine?

38:04.330 --> 38:05.530
How did

38:05.690 --> 38:07.100
your head condition suddenly flare up,

38:07.100 --> 38:08.420
making you fall ill?

38:10.170 --> 38:10.970
Could it be...

38:11.550 --> 38:12.290
Could it be

38:12.500 --> 38:13.580
that you consumed something

38:13.580 --> 38:15.590
you shouldn't have?

38:18.290 --> 38:19.330
It was you...

38:20.690 --> 38:21.650
It was you.

38:21.920 --> 38:23.250
-It was you...
-Mother,

38:23.670 --> 38:25.690
it was clearly your own carelessness.

38:25.690 --> 38:27.290
How can you blame me?

38:29.590 --> 38:30.560
Mother,

38:30.670 --> 38:32.230
do you still remember

38:32.570 --> 38:33.400
saying

38:33.530 --> 38:35.090
the exact same thing to me

38:35.340 --> 38:36.730
back then

38:36.920 --> 38:39.130
when I had my miscarriage?

38:43.740 --> 38:44.980
You wicked...

38:46.130 --> 38:46.770
wicked...

38:47.900 --> 38:48.500
wicked...

38:50.410 --> 38:51.730
Rest assured, Mother.

38:52.470 --> 38:54.790
If anything happens to you,

38:55.620 --> 38:57.520
I'll help you

38:58.100 --> 39:02.130
protect this empire.

39:14.940 --> 39:16.060
Rest assured, Mother.

39:16.060 --> 39:17.640
With me here,

39:18.250 --> 39:20.020
you'll be fine.

39:20.580 --> 39:22.080
Rest well and recover.

39:33.980 --> 39:35.190
Crown Prince,

39:35.420 --> 39:36.480
come here quickly.

39:36.730 --> 39:38.590
Your grandmother is calling you.

40:11.360 --> 40:13.720
[Memorial Tablet
of Empress Dowager Li Zhen]

40:12.810 --> 40:13.380
Dan,

40:14.900 --> 40:15.940
from now on,

40:16.520 --> 40:17.900
I'm your mother.

40:31.880 --> 40:32.720
You must be

40:33.380 --> 40:34.100
obedient.
